WEBVTT

00:02.569 --> 00:04.570
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.571 --> 00:06.572
<i>Carol convinced Jodie</i>
<i>to share an apartment,</i>

00:06.573 --> 00:08.574
<i>not as lovers, but as friends,</i>

00:08.575 --> 00:11.076
<i>even though we know</i>
<i>she'd love to be lovers,</i>

00:11.077 --> 00:12.578
<i>and speaking of lovers,</i>

00:12.579 --> 00:13.579
<i>Dennis told Jodie</i>

00:13.580 --> 00:16.081
<i>he'd love to have him back.</i>

00:16.082 --> 00:18.584
<i>Father Tim decided</i>
<i>not to remain a father</i>

00:18.585 --> 00:20.085
<i>but to become a husband,</i>

00:20.086 --> 00:22.087
<i>and asked Corinne to marry him.</i>

00:22.088 --> 00:24.590
<i>Corinne loves the idea.</i>

00:24.591 --> 00:27.593
<i>Mr. Lefkowitz told Danny</i>
<i>he'd kill his entire family</i>

00:27.594 --> 00:29.595
<i>if Danny didn't marry Elaine.</i>

00:29.596 --> 00:31.597
<i>Danny said he'd love to.</i>

00:31.598 --> 00:35.100
<i>Mr. Mallu, Jessica's lawyer,</i>
<i>told Jessica he loved her,</i>

00:35.101 --> 00:37.603
<i>and Jessica would have loved</i>
<i>to have heard "not guilty"</i>

00:37.604 --> 00:39.104
<i>from the jury.</i>

00:39.105 --> 00:41.106
<i>Since she didn't,</i>
<i>she'd love to know who did it.</i>

00:41.107 --> 00:42.107
<i>Who did?</i>

00:42.108 --> 00:43.108
<i>Was it Chester?</i>

00:43.109 --> 00:44.610
<i>Jodie? Corinne?</i>

00:44.611 --> 00:46.612
<i>Benson? Burt?</i>

00:46.613 --> 00:48.113
<i>Wouldn't you love to know?</i>

00:48.114 --> 00:50.116
<i>Stay tuned for this week's</i>
<i>episode of...</i>

00:55.121 --> 00:57.122
<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:57.123 --> 00:59.625
<i>Jessica Tate</i>

00:59.626 --> 01:02.127
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

01:02.128 --> 01:05.631
<i>These are the Tates...</i>

01:05.632 --> 01:09.134
<i>and these are the Campbells.</i>

01:09.135 --> 01:12.137
<i>And this is</i> Soap.

01:12.138 --> 01:13.639
[♪]

01:18.645 --> 01:21.147
